  <description>
  Joomla Social Comments and Sharing module allows users to share your site content to the most popular  social sites: Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn  + add Facebook comments! 
  Features:
  - Select Icons
  - Add comments (for Facebook users)
  - Facebook Share
  - Facebook Like
  - Facebook Comment 
  - Tweet Me
  - LinkedIn Share
  - Select Module Position    
  </description>

